## 5. Cập nhật MainActivity để handle Map tab

<augment_code_snippet path="app/src/main/java/com/example/manageexpenses/activity/MainActivity.java" mode="EDIT">
```java
bottomNav.setOnItemSelectedListener(item -> {
 Fragment selected = null;
 String title = "";
 if (item.getItemId() == R.id.nav_todo) {
 selected = new TodoFragment();
 title = "To-Do List";
 } else if (item.getItemId() == R.id.nav_finance) {
 selected = new FinanceFragment();
 title = "Finance";
 } else if (item.getItemId() == R.id.nav_map) {
 selected = new MapFragment();
 title = "Map";
 } else if (item.getItemId() == R.id.nav_profile) {
 selected = new ProfileFragment();
 title = "Profile";
 }
 if (selected != null) {
 setToolbarTitle(title);
 replaceFragment(selected);
 }
 return true;
});
```
</augment_code_snippet>

